，西方國家都出唔到手幫你地。<br />\n因為白紙黑字寫明50年，西方國家好尊重合約精神。<br />\n到時只會都係變返中國，仲要一下子就變，一定好多人接受唔到。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所有問題去到最後只會追究到主權問題，唔該大家真係思考下。<br />\n仲要今次搞到咁大真係最後一次反擊同最大力量<br />\n<br />\n希望大家得閒做少少文宣係關於香港獨立，不過要soft啲係真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7df7ed0e0b1d0c5cc85948b8e1ec049d8428c65c","tid":1377761,"uid":206021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T15:07:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">全面支持730港鐵大罷工</span></span>"},{"pid":"090c3e6b430f4d3ad1a3ff8825eb7e8068a96900","tid":1377761,"uid":278893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T15:09:58.000Z","msg":"民宣"},{"pid":"96d07590207b574e4836fbd2a332044a9bf6a8a7","tid":1377761,"uid":25434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T15:10:15.000Z","msg":"狗到仆街"},{"pid":"3eb69c6362aeeb1271741c0c08eafc2520eb30e6","tid":1377761,"uid":257881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T15:10:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0e856c34b2083f5a88fbfb5f700dbf31acc38e1d","tid":1377761,"uid":237355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T15:10:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"400031c4fec0b8069f39b386818e64167ed7c061","tid":1377761,"uid":289441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T15:14:12.000Z","msg":"癡線"},{"pid":"4594821dc187e03e24da97488fff092f8ac088cc","tid":1377761,"uid":92448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dc45c0db064f29b2e94d18c18baf245000eb63e7","tid":1377761,"uid":230692,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T14:32:31.000Z","msg":"推，香港警察屌你老母"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T15:17:05.000Z","msg":"係黑警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/a